= Prerequisites
   Ruby 1.8.0 or later.
   Ruby 1.8.2 or later preferred on Windows.
   
= Synopsis
   require 'sys/host'
   include Sys

   p Host.hostname
   p Host.ip_addr

   Host.info{ |h|
      p h
   }

= Installation
== Standard (non-gem) installation
   rake test (optional)
   rake install

== Gem Installation
   rake test (optional)
   rake install_gem

= Documentation
   See the doc/host.txt file for more information.